                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Talk to administrators. If you don&rsquo;t want to do that, talk to the student leaders who are there to talk to administrators for you. Be upset. Stand up, walk away from your television set, open up the window and shout, &ldquo;I&rsquo;m mad as hell and I&rsquo;m not going to take it anymore!&rdquo;</p>
<p>As always, it&rsquo;s been my pleasure ruining your Monday morning.</p>
<p><em>Danny Lewin had a blast this semester.</em></p>
